description: The Astronomy Picture of the Day will send you the daily astronomy picture with the title and a brief description. The picture will be delivered directly to your Alex app for your viewing please. It is very easy to get started, simply ask "astro pic" for the picture or ask "astro pic", what is the picture of the day.
exampleInteractions: alexa ask astro pic for the picture
alexa ask astro pic what is the picture of the day
alexa tell astro pic to give me the picture of the day
imageAltText: Astronomy Picture of the Day icon
name: Astronomy Picture of the Day
shortDescription: Do you love space? Then check out the Astronomy Picture of the Day. Check back daily for new pictures!
